=Episode 13=

27
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:42,519
So when that time comes,

28
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,680
I'll vanish completely.

29
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,480
Right?

30
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,040
Is there any way

31
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,599
to eliminate the Night Deity within me?

32
00:01:59,879 --> 00:02:01,640
Only the Sword Master
with the Divine Sword

33
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,599
can oppose him.

34
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,319
Are you saying

35
00:02:11,159 --> 00:02:12,840
that if I lose control then,

36
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:18,120
you'll have to kill me personally?

37
00:02:25,439 --> 00:02:27,280
I'll never let my life

38
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,879
lie in someone else's hand.

39
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,800
I refuse to believe

40
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,280
there's no other way

41
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,919
to suppress him
in the vast Three Realms.

42
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,159
Nor do I.

43
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,080
We'll find a solution.

44
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:39,560
Yes.

45
00:02:45,199 --> 00:02:45,599
Right.

46
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,319
I heard

47
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,439
that descendants of Shennong
and those from Kunlun Ruins

48
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,000
possess many mystical arts.

49
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:53,599
Let's go look.

50
00:02:55,319 --> 00:02:56,240
No need to rush.

51
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:59,000
Heal your injuries first.

52
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,400
I won't travel with dead weight.

53
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,599
Rest properly first.

54
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,080
Our leader's not back.

55
00:03:25,639 --> 00:03:27,159
Please stay here for two days.

56
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,680
Once the leader returns,

57
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:29,919
I'll summon you both.

58
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:30,800
Thank you.

59
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:31,960
Suit yourself.

60
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,159
Let me do it.

61
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:52,159
Legends say the Shennong Clan nurtures
a thousand-year-old Fireflow Fungus

62
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:54,599
that can suppress demonic energy.

63
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,719
But its growth requirements
are extremely specific,

64
00:03:58,599 --> 00:04:01,159
and there's been no trace of it
in recent years.

65
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:02,400
I'm afraid...

66
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,080
Afraid of what?

67
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,159
You claimed

68
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,719
you wouldn't let your life

69
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,840
lie in someone else's hand.

70
00:04:08,159 --> 00:04:10,039
We haven't even met them yet,

71
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:12,199
but you're already doubting yourself.

72
00:04:12,879 --> 00:04:13,840
I'm not.

73
00:04:18,899 --> 00:04:19,379
Right.

74
00:04:20,259 --> 00:04:21,379
On that street earlier,

75
00:04:21,620 --> 00:04:23,060
I saw a pastry shop

76
00:04:23,699 --> 00:04:25,300
with treats I've never tried.

77
00:04:26,939 --> 00:04:28,100
Go buy some for me.

78
00:04:29,699 --> 00:04:30,339
Let's go.

79
00:04:33,259 --> 00:04:35,019
It's too far. I don't want to go.

80
00:04:36,540 --> 00:04:38,180
Fine. To thank you,

81
00:04:38,660 --> 00:04:39,420
I'll cook tonight.

82
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:40,259
How's that?

83
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:42,500
I want fish.

84
00:04:43,459 --> 00:04:44,620
Got it.

85
00:04:44,899 --> 00:04:45,420
Just wait.

86
00:05:09,819 --> 00:05:10,660
Back off!

87
00:05:12,379 --> 00:05:13,860
Whatever you are,

88
00:05:15,060 --> 00:05:17,180
I won't submit!

89
00:05:31,019 --> 00:05:31,500
Chuli?

90
00:05:32,819 --> 00:05:33,300
Chuli?

91
00:05:34,660 --> 00:05:35,139
Chuli?

92
